{"id":154213,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/facebook着眼中国/","date":"2011-05-21T23:30:54Z","modified":"2011-05-21T23:30:54Z","title":"Facebook着眼中国","content":"<p>路透社报导(中文)，Mark Zuckerberg正计划第二次中国之行，寻找进入中国的方式。Facebook首席运营官Sheryl Sandberg表示：“我们公司的任务十分明确，就是联结整个世界。如果少了中国，考虑联通整个世界是不太可能的事情。”Sandberg曾担任美国前财政部长幕僚长和前Google负责销售的高管。先前许多报导称，Sandberg与Mark Zuckerberg对如何进军中国市场存在不同的看法。但她表示自己认同中国的重要性。<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/15067386/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=Facebook%E7%9D%80%E7%9C%BC%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Finternet.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F05%2F20%2F121227%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/emailthis2.gif\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=Facebook%E7%9D%80%E7%9C%BC%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Finternet.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F05%2F20%2F121227%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/bookmark.gif\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101093303717/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/15067386/a2.htm\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101093303717/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/15067386/a2.img\" /></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=0lCSy-L4JYc:fW3ctSuUv7U:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=0lCSy-L4JYc:fW3ctSuUv7U:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" /></a>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"htt